  "text": "Cu-30vol%SiC and Cu-44vol%SiC powder mixtures were fabricated using pure Cu particles (99.9%, 1 mm and <45μm in diameter) and SiC powder. In order to investigate the effects of the SiC particle size on the microstructure of the FGM, three kinds of SiC powders with 150 μm, 50 μm and 500 nm in diameter were used. Using these powder mixtures, Cu/SiC FGM was fabricated by the centrifugal mixed-powder method using vertical-type centrifugal casting machine [CITATION_1] .",
